Bordeaux Getaway

★ 5.0 · 7 reviews · Superhost · Bedroom, France

Entire rental unit hosted by Ghazal

2 guests · 1 bedroom · 1 bed · 1 bath

Enhanced Clean · Self check-in · Free cancellation before Feb 14

Come and stay in this superb duplex T2, in the heart of the historic center of Bordeaux. Shops and restaurants are within walking distance. You will enjoy all the charms of the city, thanks to its location close to many shops, bars, and restaurants. You can access the apartment by tram A and C and bus routes 27 and 4.

  • Pets allowed
